{{Youmay|the extradimensional home of the [[Charon/Legends|Charon]] [[Subspecies/Legends|subspecies]]|the role-playing adventure [[Otherspace (adventure)|''Otherspace'']]}}
'''Otherspace''' was an alternate pocket dimension beyond both [[Realspace/Legends|realspace]] and [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]]. While it appeared to be a vast expanse of storm-gray nothingness, it did contain colored, swirling [[Nebula/Legends|nebulae]], and [[Star/Legends|stars]] which were described as "shining holes of darkness."

After members of the [[Charr Ontee]] [[Species/Legends|species]] were [[Rift Disaster|"flipped"]] into otherspace, some mutated into the [[Charon/Legends|Charon]] [[Subspecies/Legends|subspecies]], native to a [[Charon homeworld|planet]] within otherspace that was threatened by a nearby [[Black hole/Legends|black hole]]. The presence of this interstellar disturbance caused an enormous amount of stress on the Charon's part. Before long, the stress twisted their culture, giving rise to a death-worshiping religion. The members of this cult believed that it was their sacred duty to speed all life toward the [[Void of Death]]. After eradicating all of those who were unbelievers&mdash;which meant destroying all [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] life&mdash;on their homeworld, the Charon developed interstellar travel, and continued their holy mission. Eventually, all that remained in otherspace was a multitude of barren, lifeless planets and a few biologically engineered Charon [[Starship/Legends|starships]] roaming the void in search of any remaining traces of life.

Otherspace was allegedly a home for the mystical energy known as the [[anti-Force]]; one rumor within [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] was that former [[Prophets of the Dark Side|Prophet of the Dark Side]] [[Cronal]] accessed otherspace and used the anti-Force to facilitate his return from the dead.<ref name="The Imperial Warlords: Despoilers of an Empire">{{SW|url=news/the-imperial-warlords-despoilers-of-an-empire-part-3|series=The Imperial Warlords: Despoilers of an Empire|text=Part 3|nolive=1}}</ref>

